qlDescription: It is encouraged to perform these stretching quickies prior to exercising.
Try these beginner level quickies if you are just starting to work out.
Perform these quickies with solid form before moving on to higher levels.
Some of these quickies may be harder than they appear.
These quickies are definitely challenging especially when performed in a workout.
Attempt these quickies if you enjoy an extremely difficult challenge.
Give these quickies a whirl, if you're a master of calisthenics.
